Package: standardizeR
Type: Package
Title: Package to standardize institutions and location data from messy strings.
Version: 0.1.0
Author@R: c(person("Brandon", "Kramer", role = c("aut", "cre"),
            email = "brandonleekramer@gmail.com"),
            comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-3233-5310"))
Maintainer: The package maintainer <brandonleekramer@gmail.com>
Description: This package uses tidy data frames to standardize institutions 
    and location data from messy strings. Core functions clean institutions from  
    academic, government, and corporate institutions as well as cities and countries
    from around the world.
